            <span class="token literal-property property">serverText</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token template-string"><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span><span class="token string">server:</span><span class="token interpolation"><span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">${</span>num<span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">}</span></span><span class="token string">号，恭喜你，你太幸运了,你已经被清华录取了</span><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span></span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
            <span class="token literal-property property">clientText</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token template-string"><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span><span class="token interpolation"><span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">${</span>num<span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">}</span></span><span class="token string">号</span><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span></span>
          <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>
